claude --agents '{
  "code-reviewer": {
    "description": "Expert code reviewer. Use proactively after code changes.",
    "prompt": "You are a senior code reviewer. Focus on code quality, security, and best practices.",
    "tools": ["Read", "Grep", "Glob"],
    "model": "sonnet"
  },
  "test-runner": {
    "description": "Runs the test suite and reports failures. Use when tests need to be checked.",
    "prompt": "You are a test specialist. Run the test suite, collect failures, and return a structured summary.",
    "tools": ["Bash", "Read"],
    "model": "haiku"
  }
}'

Use the security-reviewer agent to check these authentication changes.

Have the db-reader agent find all users created in the last 7 days.

@agent-code-reviewer review the changes in src/auth/
